  "text": ". Analysis in Ref [CITATION_1] has shown thatL is bounded byF as: |L| \u2264 \u03b3 F |F |, for some finite positive \u03b3 F . Therefore, by selecting u rob = \u2212K rob \u03b2F , with a large feedback gain K rob > \u03b3 F ,\u1e86 total becomes:",
